features: Product Overview: This product is a high power fan power PWM hub, can help users adjust the speed of the fan and power supply, suitable for all kinds of PC equipment, PC, computer room heat dissipation, mining machine and other occasions.
Power parameters: The power voltage is 12V DC, the maximum current of the interface is 17A, and the power interface is 6pin (2x3).
Output ports: A total of 8 output ports, fan holder support 3pin and 4pin fans, can power up to 8 fans.

Speed control function: The rotating potentiometer of this product can adjust the speed of 8 PWM fans at the same time, but it should be noted that if the fan does not support PWM speed control function, the speed control function is invalid.

Installation mode: There is a bonding pad at the bottom, which can be bonded in the chassis. When using, ensure that the total current of the connected fan does not exceed the maximum current of 17A, so as to avoid damage to the governor.
body.description: Specifications: Name: High Power Fan PWM Hub Governor Size: 42 x 29 x 20mm/1.65 x 1.14 x 0.79inch Weight: 12g Power supply voltage: DC12V Power interface: 6PIN (2 x 3) Maximum interface current: 17A Number of fan bases: 8 Package includes: 1 high-power fan PWM hub governor Characteristic: The power supply voltage of this product is 12V DC, the maximum current of the interface is 17A, and the power interface is 6pin (2x3). This product has a total of 8 output interfaces, and the fan base supports 3pin and 4pin fans, which can power up to 8 fans. Be careful: The speed regulation function of this product requires the fan to support PWM speed regulation function, otherwise it cannot be achieved. Meanwhile, please ensure that the total current connected to the fan does not exceed the maximum current value of 17A during use to avoid damage to the governor.
